01:42:51.624 --> 01:42:53.489
Andy!

1764
01:42:56.253 --> 01:42:59.245
It's all right, Andy.
It's just bolognese!

1765
01:43:59.692 --> 01:44:01.603
How's lurch?
He's in the freezer.

1766
01:44:01.694 --> 01:44:02.900
